data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own a direct bayfront double unit at almost 4,000 sqft of space! Many updates in the last 1-2 years, including most flooring, new porcelain tile, gorgeous new Kitchen with marble counters with stone accents, new half bath added, total remodeled Primary Bath with copper freestanding tub, new windows, 2 new water heaters & 1 HVAC unit. Don't miss the incredible & spacious library /den with custom mahogany woodwork, gas fireplace, wet bar, wine frig, and balcony overlooking the Bay! The Kitchen & Dining & Great rooms are open w/bay views from all rooms. Freshly painted throughout, 3 total gas fireplaces, 2 covered reserved parking spaces, elevator, and more. Call today to schedule your private showing.
